snippet.title: Coof Attack Trailer
snippet.description:
Get it now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1283260/Coof_Attack

Defend your toilet paper from an ever-growing angry mob! Even the odds by teaming up with friends in up to 4-player co-op. Customise your character's appearance and skills to fit your play-style. Discover more as you progress and unlock even cooler stuff.

Check out the store page for more info!
